    "summary": "This paper demonstrates a two-site Kitaev chain built from Yu-Shiba-Rusinov (YSR) states in proximitized InSb quantum dots coupled through a common superconducting hybrid segment. By tuning the hybridization to the superconducting segment, the authors realize poor man’s Majorana zero modes with a larger excitation gap (~76 \u0003bc eV) and much reduced sensitivity to charge noise compared with earlier quantum-dot-based implementations.",
